metadata.name: Cubicula
metadata.description:
Virtuality is a spell of a long natural homeorhesis; what seems to be a limited, soulless and claustrophobic environment is just a genesis phase, response and adaptation of synthetic matter emerging from a stress state created by ourselves.

Cubicula represents a close flyby of the staminal blocks of this new emerging branch of development, showing the landscape of stems scattered and clumped together in complex inscrutable dimensional ambients.

Concept, visuals and music: Daniel Oakfield
